dct_title_s: Nova totius Livoniae accurata descriptio.; Nova totivs Livoniae accvrata descriptio
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes ship illustrations on the ocean and fruits around the title cartouche. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636 and 1637. From the Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 55 x 44 cm.
dct_creator_sm: Hondius, Hendrik, 1597-1651. Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe
Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas of the British Isles and Northern Europe
